SHADOW (34)<br>
<br>
witch king, lord of the nazgul x 2<br>
otsea, lietenant of morgul x 3<br>
nelya, twilight x 2<br>
enquea, lieutenant x 2<br>
cantea, lieutenant x 2<br>
